These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
House: cape-cod, craftsman, farmhouse, colonial
1. the craftsman house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
2. the person eating mango is the colonial house##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the colonial house##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| House   | craftsman  | cape-cod     | farmhouse   | colonial |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, western, spy, satire
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person watching western movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy    | western      | mystery | satire |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, cricket, basketball, sailing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Sport         | snowboarding | sailing | basketball   | cricket |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, drama, western
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, snake, cat, fish
1. the owner of the snake is the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | western | disaster | action  | drama      |
| Pet         | snake | fish   | cat | guinea-pig |

