.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, designer, chef, nurse
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, hedgehog, pony
1. the designer is on the left of the electrician##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the chef##1
3. the nurse is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Job   | nurse | chef | designer | electrician |
| Pet    | dog       | pony | hedgehog | hamster     |

