The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, family, thriller, time-travel
1. the mexican is on the far right##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | nigerian | dutch | mexican |
| Movie-Genre           | western      | thriller | time-travel | family    |

