.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, spy, zombie
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk, cola, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | spy       | family | zombie   |
| Beverage     | almond-milk | cola | hot-chocolate   | fanta |

