2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Pet    | bird | rat  | horse | hamster |
| Transport   | tram | train | taxi          | bus    |

