.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, sprite, water
House: farmhouse, modern, craftsman, victorian
1. the craftsman house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
2. the victorian house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking milk is the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | sprite | milk  | hot-chocolate | water |
| House   | farmhouse  | craftsman | victorian           | modern   |

