3. the person traveling to rome is the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |     4      |
| City          | colone | marseilles  | rome  | hamburg |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | comedy | horror | thriller   |

