.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, weightlifting, basketball, swimming
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, scooter, snowmobile
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Sport   | skateboarding | basketball | weightlifting | swimming   |
| Transport     | scooter  | boat    | car       | snowmobile |

 